data.description: Location… Location… Location… The Home Has A Special PROPERTY TAX REDUCTION (ABATEMENT) FOR THE NEXT 10 YEARS! Beautiful is best way to describe this home nestled blocks away from the 18th & Vine area where there are Museums & BBQ to enjoy. It isn't far from the Plaza and Westport entertainment areas. Just seconds away from the highway and walking distance from Spring Valley Park.  This beautifully updated property has new Electrical, HVAC and a New Roof.  What are you waiting for… Come see this beautiful home that has the Master located on the first floor and laundry located on the same floor as well.  The covered porch has thermal windows and LED canister lights!  This Is The Beautiful Must See Home, That Your Family Is Waiting For!
